  "body": "<p>One of my favorite products that Amy has released has got to be the <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B00I99RKI4/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=B00I99RKI4&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=wwwamytangeri-20&amp;linkId=K5FGNEFSWAZ7ASGF\">stitching templates</a>! I love making fun, simple, one of a kind cards using nothing more than the template, some thread and white card stock. Sometimes I will also add a small sentiment as well, but seriously folks it doesn't get easier! </p><p>I start with my card base and decide which template to use. For this baby shower card  (baby boy!) I decided to use blues and greens so I picked out some of my favorites from my thread stash (this is actually the kids friendship bracelet kit, don't tell anyone!).</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/75b63f7fca199f77.jpg?v=1782526809\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Once I have pierced the holes using the Amy Tangerine template I just started with one balloon and worked my way around. I love that the balloons have the stripes, it just adds a special little touch! I am a fan of using washi on the back side to secure everything, easy and FUN!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"5b-B2.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/c0489817af029b91.jpg?v=1782526812\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"5c-B3.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/0c16284dd646a162.jpg?v=1782526814\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"5d-B4.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/8a23b75bf780a95b.jpg?v=1782526817\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"5e-b5.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/3c54190436808e83.jpg?v=1782526820\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"5f-b6.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/ad1e68982646db99.jpg?v=1782526822\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"5g-B7.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/51847ec2660ff060.jpg?v=1782526826\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"5h-B8.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/b4c94139025fcda9.jpg?v=1782526828\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Once I was done with the balloons I added a little bow made out of the same thread I used of bows and just a touch of hot glue. I kept the sentiment super simple so that the balloons are the star of the show! Once I was done with the front I simple added a piece of scrap paper to the back to cover up my hot mess and a hand written note to wrap it up! </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/b68931d4f85708c1.jpg?v=1782526831\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>What I love most about these templates is that I can make dozens of these cards with these templates and now that I have my basic design down it will be amazingly simple!!</p><p><em>Love the colors and stitching! Thanks for sharing, </em><a href=\"http://shannanoel.blogspot.com/\"><em>Shanna</em></a><em>! Shop for Amy Tangerine products at your local scrapbook stores and online at </em><a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=simon%20home%20page&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom\"><em>Simon Says Stamp</em></a><em> and </em><a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=213361&amp;m=25838&amp;afftrack=Amy%20tangerine&amp;urllink=www%2Ebluemoonscrapbooking%2Ecom%2FCategoryProductList%2Ejsp%3Fcat%3DShop%253AManufacturers%253AAmerican%2BCrafts%3AAmerican%2BCrafts%2BAmy%2BTangerine\"><em>Blue Moon Scrapbooking</em></a><em> and </em><a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=33086&amp;m=7429&amp;afftrack=&amp;urllink=store%2Escrapbook%2Ecom%2Fproducts%2F%3Fw%3Damy%2Btangerine\"><em>Scrapbook.com</em></a><em>. </em></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
